Analysis Report on the WeRateDogs Twitter Using Twitters API¶

The datasets involved in this analysis are:

  • The WeRateDogs Twitter archive dataset
  • The Image prediction dataset
  • The Tweet likes and retweet dataset

I wrangled this datasets by:

  • Gathering: which involved downloading Manually, downloading programmatically using Requests library and using the Twitter API.
  • Accessing: which involved both Visual accessment and programmatic accessment to find the Quality and tidiness issues.
  • Cleaning: which involved rectifying the issues discovered during the Accessment phase.
  • Storing: hich involved storing the cleaned dataset as twitter-master-archive.csv.

When I was done with storing the cleaned dataset I went ahead to analysis it so as to get insights from the data set and I had the following findings:

Insight¶

  • The most retweeted tweet was of a Labrador retriever
  • The top rated dog was a Labrador retriever
  • The most popular dog type that was tweeted was the golden retriever
  • Tweet with the highest number of likes
  • Tweet with the lowest number of likes

Visuals¶

  • The most retweeted dog state
  • The most popular dog names
